@startuml

participant uv_shell as us
participant runtime_daemon as rd
participant shmQueueThread as sqt
queue h2fQueue as h2fq
queue f2hQueue as f2hq
participant FileProcess as fp

== start process ==

us --> rd: <<connect>>
us --> rd: <<utilization>>
rd --> rd++ #green: setUserAccount()
    rd --> rd++: make_shared<UserAccount>
        rd --> rd: <<create shm>>
        rd --> rd: <<create shm>>
        rd --> fp: <<fork with key of shm>>
        rd --> rd: <<create h2fqueue>>
        rd --> rd: <<create f2hqueue>>
        rd --> sqt: <<invoke>>

        fp --> fp: sleep 1s
        fp --> fp: interface = make_shared<Interface>
        fp <-- h2fq: load_h2fq
        fp <-- f2hq: load_f2hq
        fp --> fp: setgroups()
        fp --> fp: setgid()
        fp --> fp: setegid()
        fp --> fp: setuid()


== io req process ==
        loop #lightblue handle file io req
            rd --> rd++: HostIO::open
            note right
                返回值：logic fd，屏蔽真实的fd
                问题：fileprocess返回fd，response如何找到调用者？
                方案：所有的请求包与回包都会携带logic_fd
            end note

                rd <-- h2fq: interface->h2fquque.peek()
                rd --> h2fq: interface->h2fquque.send()
            return
            rd --> rd: thread_meta_data->m_cv.wait_for(timeout)
            fp <-- h2fq: interface->h2fq.try_pop(buf)
            fp --> fp++: handle()
                ...
                fp --> f2hq: peek()
                fp --> f2hq: send()
            return
            fp --> h2fq: ack()

            sqt <-- f2hq: pop(buf)
            sqt --> rd: notify()

            rd --> rd: <<read buf>>

            note right
            1、关键数据结构thread_meta_data
            2、标记每个io req，fileprocess回包时能找到正确的调用者
            
            end note

        end loop

    return
return



@enduml